a person or being completely without malice, whose nature is loving or caring.\n\n====Name origin====\nLuvdisc and Lovecus is a combination of \'\'love\'\' and \'\'{{wp|discus (fish)|discus}}\'\' or \'\'disc\'\' (in reference to its thin, flat body).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Water|type2=Water\n|ja=ラブカス \'\'Lovecus\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'love\'\' and \'\'discus\'\'\n|de=Liebiskus|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Liebe|love}}\'\', \'\'{{tt|Diskus|discus}}\'\', and \'\'{{tt|Hibiskus|hibiscus}}\'\'\n|fr=Lovdisc|frmeaning=From \'\'love\'\' and \'\'discus\'\' or \'\'disc\'\'. Similar to English name\n|es=Luvdisc|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|it=Luvdisc|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=사랑동이 \'\'Sarangdongi\'\'|komeaning=Combination of {{tt|사랑 \'\'sarang\'\'|love}} and {{tt|동이 \'\'dong\'i\'\'|diminutive suffix}}\n|zh_cmn=愛心魚 / 爱心鱼 \'\'Ài Xīn Yú\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Literally "Love fish".\n|hi=लाभडिस्क \'\'Luvdisc\'\'|himeaning=Transliteration of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Caserin and Luverin]]\n<!--\n===Notes===\n<references />-->\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Water}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Water|prevnum=369|prev=Relicanth|nextnum=371|next=Bagon}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Liebiskus]]\n[[es:Luvdisc]]\n[[fr:Lovdisc]]\n[[it:Luvdisc]]\n[[ja:ラブカス]]\n[[zh:爱心鱼]]'}